column2: Slight overcast.  Pristine day.  Wildlife abounds.
Some humidity.  Lightly fished.  Some wildlife.
Quiet and cool.  Full autumn colors.
Cool.  Believe lake has flip flopped.
Partly cloudy day.  Slight chop on water surface.
Partly cloudy day.  Water surface choppy.  Windy.
Bright sunny day- this is the first cool day after hot humid weather.  Boating traffic is very light.  Could not find 13' hole.
Sunny day and the water surface is fairly smooth.
Sunny day. water surface choppy.  Windy.  Last test of this year.
Bright sunny day.  45 F.  Cold weather is setting in.  Very few boats out.
Very windy and some white caps. Very difficult to get a good depth reading.
Sunny- light breeze- moderate boat traffic.
Sunny- light breeze- moderate boat traffic.
Partly cloudy- light breeze.  No boat traffic.
Sunny- light breeze- no boat traffic.  Rained on and off yesterday.
Sunny and cool day.  Put boat away for the season.
Water had a slight chop. First check for 2001.
Sunny- warm- breezy.  Low boat traffic.
Partly sunny- warm- breezy.  Rained about 1" yesterday.  Moderate boat traffic.
Sunny- warm- humid.  No rain lately.  Moderate boat traffic.
Partly sunny- overcast.  Warm- humid.  76 F air temp.  No rain for 2 weeks.
Partly cloudy day- smooth water. Very little boat traffic.
Sunny- warm- light breeze.  Has been hot and humid for the last 9 days.  Boat traffic low.
Sunny day- a few clouds. Water smooth. Very little boat traffic.
Overcast- light boat traffic.  Visible bloom.
Partly cloudy day- little wind. Last observation- taking pontoon out of water.
Partly sunny.  No boat traffic.  Rained yesterday 2".
Sunny- cold- temperature is 34 degrees- and there is a light breeze.
Partly cloudy- but sunny during testing.  Light boat traffic.  No rain for 48 hours.
Intermittent clouds- sunny during test.  Light boat traffic- no rain days.
Sunny- no boat traffic- light rain yesterday- windy.
Cloudy- no boat traffic- slight breeze.
Sunny and windy.  68 F.  No rain for 4 days.
Sunny and light wind.  69 F.  Rain / storm last evening.
Partly sunny and windy.  64 F.  Rained overnight.
Windy- sunny- light rain this morning.
Bright sunny day- no recent rain.  Warm.  Little boat traffic.
Bright sunny day.  Light boat traffic.  No rain in 4 days.  Warm.
Overcast day.  Light boat traffic.  Rained 1/2 inch yesterday.  Light breeze.
Bright sunny day.  Calm.  No recent rain.  Very little boat traffic.
Sunny. Rained and t'storms yesterday. Low boat traffic
Cold snap for 3 days (~25F at night) minimal boat traffic- sunny- snowed yesterday
